        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Anywhere near the DS zone-in, maybe not towards the left where the goranga camp is. They do a lot of pacing back and forth so you don't really have to worry about where they will end up. Zone gets trained a lot, everyone should be aware of this so peak hours would be a risky time to try.</P><P>Abaraxas Malfoy<BR>Warlock of the Tribunal<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
